Splitting the Dataset into Train and Test (60:40) datasets

set.seed(12345)
train.rows = sample(rownames(df), dim(df)[1]*0.6)
train.df = df[train.rows, ]

valid.rows = setdiff(rownames(df), train.rows) 
valid.df = df[valid.rows, ]
